There are many many more warnings like that. I'm not sure what these warnings mean and google isn't being very helpful.  I have two questions:

1) Should I worry about these warnings?

2) Is there a way to get rid of these warnings? They really clutter up the build log and make it hard to pick out other (more serious?) issues that might exist in the code.

Thanks!
